lead_paragraph: The Chicago Cubs lavished Jon Lester with a $155 million contract in the winter of 2014 precisely for moments like the one he faced Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Lester Falters as Cubs Lose to Indians 6-0 in Series Opener
